    <string name="text_view_long">
        This acts as a terminal output which writes the relevant info regarding the Pulse
        service including the followings:

        \n\nService scheduled:\nShows whether the service is set for repetition.

        \n\n# of POI:\nNumber of boundaries of interest (polygons) in the JSON file.

        \n\nLast location:\nOn startup, this shows the last known location found by the service but
        as soon as the next pulse is sent, it gets updated to the most current location.

        \n\nSecret:\nAn array whose length is equal to number of POIs and contains zeros and ones
        indicating whether the location falls into any of the POIs or not.
        \n\n
    </string>

